From 07b93a5704b0b72002f0c4bd1076214af67dc661 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Mario Limonciello <mario.limonciello@amd.com>
Date: Thu, 24 Jul 2025 15:00:43 -0500
Subject: [PATCH] drm/amd/display: Avoid a NULL pointer dereference
Git-commit: 07b93a5704b0b72002f0c4bd1076214af67dc661
Patch-mainline: v6.17-rc3
Alt-commit: 1e5e8d672fec9f2ab352be121be971877bff2af9
References: stable-fixes CVE-2025-39693 bsc#1249279

[WHY]
Although unlikely drm_atomic_get_new_connector_state() or
drm_atomic_get_old_connector_state() can return NULL.

[HOW]
Check returns before dereference.

